{"lastModified":1764620529394,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer/Winter Operating Area: U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands\n\nKoru is a remarkable Catana catamaran crafted for those who seek both performance and luxury.\nSpend your days moving with the sun: enjoy breakfast on the flybridge, lunch in the forward lounge, and dinner in the spacious outdoor saloon as the sky turns gold. Lounge on the expansive, cushioned foredeck for stargazing and movie nights under the open sky. Below deck, three large queen staterooms feature walk-around beds, separate dry heads, and full showers—ensuring privacy and comfort throughout your journey.\nDip your toes in the water off the swim platform while sipping cocktails while the kids wakeboard in the balmy late afternoon. When it’s time to sail, Koru delivers—with a powerful square-topped mainsail, self-tacking jib, and a 90 sqm Code 0 for light air conditions. Whether you’re chasing the horizon or simply unwinding in style, Koru is more than a yacht—it’s your floating sanctuary of adventure and ease.","blueprint":{"name":"KORU","images":["/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8B3a-7BXP.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-npLzKOwDDl.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-6MndIEd-Ng.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-j9GAaKrlm.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-C7th0uc4H.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-20v28LjtM.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::2a16d460-b655-11f0-b4ad-eb473fcfec5f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-wR3muocNh.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-Ph-YGwgl5s.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-UQJeRpNs1.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-4ON-79q4ys.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-E0mGydnyKs.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-100082-Whd2S9kGL.jpg/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Catana","model":"","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":6,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::27c2908a-b3ee-11ed-b78d-325096b39f47","name":"Saint Thomas","coordinates":{"latitude":18.34577280760982,"longitude":-64.92915768977362},"country":"US Virgin Islands"},"builtYear":2021,"topSpeed":8,"cruiseSpeed":7,"cabins":3,"bathrooms":3,"length":14.94,"beam":7.88,"draft":1.35,"hullType":"Catamaran","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x Yanmar 57HP","amenities":[{"label":"Air conditioning"},{"label":"Deck shower"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Sailing Instructions"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Hammock"},{"label":"Ice Maker"},{"label":"Generator"},{"label":"Special Diets"},{"label":"Sun Awning"}],"toys":[{"label":"Kneeboard","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"Floating Mats"},{"label":"Boarding Ladder (Off Scoop Steps)"},{"label":"Beach Games"},{"label":"Stand up paddle boards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":"Deep Sea Fish"},{"label":"Underwater Video"},{"label":"Sea Scooters"},{"label":"Kite Boarding"},{"label":"Assorted board games"},{"label":"Beach shade and rugs"}],"entertainment":["Onboard Wi-Fi","Salon Stereo","Salon TV","iPod/Device Hookups","40\" 4K Smart TV - Netflix, Disney+, Amazon Prime and more subscriptions"],"tenders":["12ft Dinghy with 40 HP engine (6 pax)"]},"crew":[{"name":"Benjamin Nucci","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e13eb790-b653-11f0-b4ad-eb473fcfec5f/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I grew up in Canada surrounded by nature and spent my summers exploring its beautiful lakes, where my love for boating and adventure began. I’ve always enjoyed being on the water, whether it’s cruising, wakeboarding, tubing, or just soaking up the sun. I’m passionate about creating a fun and relaxed atmosphere onboard, making sure everyone feels included and has a great time. When I’m not sailing, I love sharing stories, good music, and a few laughs with guests. My goal is to make every trip memorable, with a perfect balance of adventure, connection, and laid-back enjoyment."},{"name":"Juan Ramirez","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4e05-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::039a3030-b654-11f0-b4ad-eb473fcfec5f/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"I’m Chef Juan Ramirez, and for me, cooking is all about connection , bringing people together through food, stories, and shared experiences at sea. With over eight years in hospitality, I’ve cooked across Europe, America, and Asia, learning to blend global flavors with local Caribbean ingredients. I truly love what I do and I bring warmth, creativity and care to every dish. Whether it’s an elegant dinner or a casual beach barbecue, my goal is to make guests feel at home, happy, and completely cared for."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":2000000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":2000000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","pr